reviews.text: One of the best Japanese food in Shatin, Hong Kong

Chefs and Staffs are super friendly 
Had a amazing lunch there 
Lunch teppanyaki set was money for value
Presentation is more than expected
Chefs have great cooking skill
Definitely will come back again for meal
Recommend for celebration and dating night

This excellent restaurant has never once disappointed over the many many years.  Food is always fresh and top quality, service is always excellent, the seafood teppanyaki (especially the lobster and abalone) is their specialty as is their Kobe beef. You're in for a treat here
Unexpected！ Good Service ,Great Ingredients , Delicious 😋

Don’t be distracted by the slightly outdated decor and humble exterior. We have patroned his place for ten years now and we think it’s one of the best Japanese restaurant in Hong Kong and at a reasonable price. The standard is consistent at any time of the year, lunch and dinner. The sashimi is as fresh as you would get in japan. The teppanyaki chefs are as good as in Ropongi and the food always fresh. The staff are helpful and anticipating. My husband and I love this place !
